<% content_for :title do %>MIT Model United Nations Conference &mdash; Committees<% end %>
<div class="container container-main">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col">
      <h1 class="title">MITMUNC XII 2020 Committees</h1>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col">
      <p>MITMUNC features many different committees that embark on a wide array of enthralling topics past, present, and future.</p>
      <h4>Position Paper Guidelines</h4>
      <p>Unless the relevant committee&rsquo;s background guide specifies otherwise, position papers should follow these guidelines:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>One page for each topic.</li>
        <li>12-point font, single-spaced.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Delegates should email their completed position paper <strong>by January 13</strong> to the email address of their specific committee.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div id="committeeAccordion" class="col">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="btn btn-outline-primary text-left" data-target="#ASEAN" data-toggle="collapse">
          <h3>Association of Southeast Asian Nations (ASEAN)</h3>
